INSERT INTO `vendor_listings` VALUES (1,15,'Party Poppers PH','Makati City','NCR','Metro Manila','Makati City','Decoration','Party Squad PH specializes in creative event styling and venue decorations for birthdays, weddings, corporate events, and themed parties. Their decoration packages start at ₱10,000, which includes a basic backdrop setup, balloon arrangements, and simple table centerpieces.\r\n\r\nFor more detailed and customized themes, their styling packages range from ₱15,000 to ₱30,000, depending on the venue size and design requirements. These packages may include themed stage backdrops, balloon installations, entrance décor, ceiling treatments, and photo area setups.\r\n\r\nAdditional add-ons such as LED lights, personalized signage, and upgraded floral arrangements are available for an extra fee.','Party Squad PH specializes in creative event styling and venue decorations for birthdays, weddings, corporate events, and themed parties. Their decoration packages start at ₱10,000, which includes a basic backdrop setup, balloon arrangements, and simple table centerpieces.\n\nFor more detailed and customized themes, their styling packages range from ₱15,000 to ₱30,000, depending on the venue size and design requirements. These packages may include themed stage backdrops, balloon installations, entrance décor, ceiling treatments, and photo area setups.\n\nAdditional add-ons such as LED lights, personalized signage, and upgraded floral arrangements are available for an extra fee.','Party Squad PH provides event decoration and styling services for birthdays, weddings, corporate events, and other celebrations. They create themed backdrops, balloon setups, table decorations, and photo areas to make the venue look beautiful and organized. Their team focuses on simple, creative designs that match the client’s theme and budget, helping turn any space into a fun and memorable event setting.','https://res.cloudinary.com/dm60rzkyp/image/upload/v1770743405/solennia/vendor